# Stan dashboard environment variables
#
# Google Maps JavaScript API key (optional).
# - If set, the dashboard renders Google Maps with road-following routes.
# - If left empty/unset, the dashboard falls back to the free Leaflet/OSM map.
#
# Create the key in Google Cloud Console (Maps JavaScript API + Directions API
# enabled) and restrict it to your dashboard's domain (HTTP referrer).
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in the value. Never commit the real ".env".
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
